data.description: SELLER WILLING TO OFFER $5,000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS!! WATER HEATER INSTALLED THIS YEAR* HVAC INSTALLED 2021 & SERVICED THIS YEAR * ROOF UNDER 10 YEARS OLD!! Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch style home nestled in the heart of Fayetteville. With a generous living space of 1,552 square feet, this residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and timeless appeal. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a neatly landscaped front yard and a welcoming entrance. The front porch, a charming introduction to the home, offers a tranquil spot to pause and appreciate the natural surroundings. Stepping inside, an inviting open-concept layout seamlessly blends the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The spacious living room offers an inviting ambiance that's perfect for gatherings and relaxation. Step into the heart of the home where the kitchen seamlessly opens to the living room, creating a harmonious flow that's perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. The kitchen features a collection of stainless-steel appliances that beautifully elevate the space. With its open layout, cooking becomes a social affair, allowing you to interact with guests or keep an eye on family activities while preparing delicious meals. This inviting space merges the culinary and living areas, making it easy to whip up a gourmet meal while staying connected to the vibrant energy of the living room. Adjacent to the kitchen and living room, a charming guest bedroom welcomes you with open arms. Bathed in the sun's gentle embrace, this room brings the outdoors inside, surrounding you with a comforting glow as you enter. Its generous windows flood the space with natural light, creating a serene ambiance that transforms this bedroom into a peaceful haven for guests. Here, you can relish the beauty of every season, from the blossoming vibrancy of spring to the cozy golden tones of autumn. Two welcoming guest bedrooms are conveniently located to share a well-appointed hall bathroom. This arrangement ensures that comfort and accessibility are seamlessly integrated. Nestled peacefully at the rear of the house, the master suite offers a serene escape. This private space brings relaxation to the forefront, providing a perfect sanctuary from life's demands. Whether in search of tranquility or a restful night's sleep, the master suite has been carefully arranged to cater to your comfort. Step into the charmingly updated master bathroom, a delightful retreat that has been thoughtfully revitalized to enhance your daily routines. The bathroom showcases brand new vinyl flooring that adds both charm and coziness underfoot. The introduction of a fresh vanity brings a touch of sophistication and practicality, offering ample room for your daily essentials. Additionally, the walk-in shower has been tastefully modernized, ensuring a relaxing experience. This master bathroom has been crafted with utmost care, ensuring that every detail contributes to a comforting and convenient ambiance. Step into the backyard, a secluded oasis that invites outdoor gatherings. The patio area is perfect for enjoying meals in the fresh air, while the expansive yard provides ample space for gardening, recreational activities, or the possibility of adding a personal touch like a charming fire pit. Additionally, the backyard features an in-ground saltwater pool, offering a refreshing retreat during warmer months. For added privacy and security, the backyard is fully fenced, creating a safe haven for your enjoyment. This home offers easy access to local amenities, schools, parks, and major roadways, making daily commutes and errands a breeze. Whether you're seeking a tranquil suburban haven or a place to build cherished memories, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home embodies the quintessential blend of comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own and experience the best of Fayetteville living. Schedule your appointment today!
